[25.731531, "o", "\u001b[40m\u001b[1;101H  \u001b[97m## Where each surface reads what\u001b[39m                                                                 \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[2;101H                                                                                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[3;101H  \u001b[97m| Surface | What it shows / consumes |\u001b[39m                                                           \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[4;101H  \u001b[97m|---|---|\u001b[39m                                                                                        \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[5;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm` TUI QA pane (`q`) | Three categories listed inline (Instructions, Regression Tests, \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[6;101H  \u001b[97mArtifact Recipes); mocks have their own CLI surface via `pm qa mocks`. Reads `title`, \u001b[39m           \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[7;101H  \u001b[97m`description` for display. |\u001b[39m                                                                     \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[8;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa list` | Same three sections as the QA pane. |\u001b[39m                                           \u001b["]
[25.731557, "o", "49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[9;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa show <id>` | Full body of one file; auto-detects category. |\u001b[39m                            \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[10;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa edit <id>` | Opens the file in `$EDITOR`; auto-detects category. |\u001b[39m                      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[11;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-instruction <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/instructions/`. |\u001b[39m                  \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[12;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-regression <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/regression/`. |\u001b[39m                     \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[13;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-artifact <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/artifacts/`. |\u001b[39m                        \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[14;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-instruction <name>` | Same as add-instruction, but launches a guided Claude \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[15;101H  \u001b[97msession that uses this document to interview the author. |\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[16;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-regression <name>` | Guided authoring for a regression test. |\u001b[3"]
[25.731566, "o", "9m                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[17;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-artifact <name>` | Guided authoring for an artifact recipe. |\u001b[39m                    \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[18;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa docs` | Prints this document. |\u001b[39m                                                         \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[19;101H  \u001b[97m| QA planner prompt | `instruction_summary_for_prompt` renders `### Instructions` and `### \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[20;101H  \u001b[97mArtifact Recipes`. Recipes are referenced by filename in the scenario `INSTRUCTION:` field. |\u001b[39m    \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[21;101H  \u001b[97m| Scenario 0 prompt | Same library summary, scoped to the interactive session. |\u001b[39m                 \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[22;101H  \u001b[97m| Bug-fix flow prompt | Points sessions at `pm/qa/instructions/` and `pm/qa/artifacts/` by \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[23;101H  \u001b[97mdirectory; sessions discover specific files themselves. Captures go under \u001b[39m                       \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[24;101H  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/pre-fix/` and `вҖҰ/post-fix/"]
