[34.589262, "o", "                          \u001b[23;51H                                                 \u001b[24;51H                                                 \u001b[25;51H                                                 \u001b[26;51H                                                 \u001b[27;51H                                                 \u001b[28;51H                                                 \u001b[29;51H                                                 \u001b[30;51H                                                 \u001b[31;51H                                                 \u001b[32;51H                                                 \u001b[33;51H                                                 \u001b[34;51H                                                 \u001b[35;51H                                                 \u001b[36;51H                                                 \u001b[37;51H                                                 \u001b[38;51H                                                 \u001b[39;51H                                                 \u001b[40;51H                     "]
[34.589282, "o", "                            \u001b[41;51H                                                 \u001b[42;51H                                                 \u001b[43;51H                                                 \u001b[44;51H                                                 \u001b[45;51H                                                 \u001b[46;51H                                                 \u001b[47;51H                                                 \u001b[48;51H                                                 \u001b[49;51H                                                 \u001b[40m\u001b[1;101H  \u001b[97m|---|---|\u001b[39m                                                                                        \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[2;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm` TUI QA pane (`q`) | Three categories listed inline (Instructions, Regression Tests, \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[3;101H  \u001b[97mArtifact Recipes); mocks have their own CLI surface via `pm qa mocks`. Reads `title`, \u001b[39m           \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[4;101H  \u001b[97m`description` for display. |\u001b[39m                                        "]
[34.589301, "o", "                             \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[5;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa list` | Same three sections as the QA pane. |\u001b[39m                                           \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[6;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa show <id>` | Full body of one file; auto-detects category. |\u001b[39m                            \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[7;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa edit <id>` | Opens the file in `$EDITOR`; auto-detects category. |\u001b[39m                      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[8;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-instruction <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/instructions/`. |\u001b[39m                  \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[9;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-regression <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/regression/`. |\u001b[39m                     \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[10;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa add-artifact <name>` | Scaffolds a stub in `pm/qa/artifacts/`. |\u001b[39m                        \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[11;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-instruction <name>` | Same as add-instruction, but launches a guided Claude \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[12;101H  \u001b[97msession that uses this document to interview the autho"]
[34.589319, "o", "r. |\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[13;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-regression <name>` | Guided authoring for a regression test. |\u001b[39m                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[14;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-artifact <name>` | Guided authoring for an artifact recipe. |\u001b[39m                    \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[15;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa docs` | Prints this document. |\u001b[39m                                                         \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[16;101H  \u001b[97m| QA planner prompt | `instruction_summary_for_prompt` renders `### Instructions` and `### \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[17;101H  \u001b[97mArtifact Recipes`. Recipes are referenced by filename in the scenario `INSTRUCTION:` field. |\u001b[39m    \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[18;101H  \u001b[97m| Scenario 0 prompt | Same library summary, scoped to the interactive session. |\u001b[39m                 \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[19;101H  \u001b[97m| Bug-fix flow prompt | Points sessions at `pm/qa/instructions/` and `pm/qa/artifacts/` by \u001b[39m      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[20;101H  \u001b[97mdirectory; sessions discover s"]
[34.589339, "o", "pecific files themselves. Captures go under \u001b[39m                       \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[21;101H  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/pre-fix/` and `вҖҰ/post-fix/`. |\u001b[39m                                      \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[22;101H  \u001b[97m| Bug-fix review checklist | Tells reviewers to read captures under \u001b[39m                             \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[23;101H  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/`. |\u001b[39m                                                                \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[24;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks list/show/add/edit` | CLI for `pm/qa/mocks/`. |\u001b[39m                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[25;101H  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks prompt` | Prints the block injected into every QA scenario prompt. |\u001b[39m              \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[26;101H                                                                                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[27;101H  \u001b[97m## Authoring tips\u001b[39m                                                                                \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[28;101H                     "]
[34.589362, "o", "                                                                              \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[29;101H  \u001b[97m- For artifact recipes, the manifest format section is the most\u001b[39m                                  \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[30;101H  \u001b[97m  load-bearing part вҖ” make it unambiguous so captures aren't opaque.\u001b[39m                             \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[31;101H  \u001b[97m- Recipes can reference your project's own paths and tooling freely вҖ”\u001b[39m                            \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[32;101H  \u001b[97m  the QA library is per-project. Only extract something into a recipe\u001b[39m                            \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[33;101H  \u001b[97m  if you'll reuse it across multiple scenarios or PRs.\u001b[39m                                           \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[34;101H  \u001b[97m- `pm qa list` shows existing recipes; `pm qa show <id>` prints any\u001b[39m                              \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[35;101H  \u001b[97m  one of them. Browse a few before authoring something new вҖ” the\u001b[39m                                 \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[36;101H "]
[34.589379, "o", " \u001b[97m  fastest way to learn the shape is to read what's already there.\u001b[39m                                \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[37;101H                                                                                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[40m\u001b[38;101H                                                                                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[K\u001b[39;101H\u001b[K\u001b[37m\nв—Ҹ\u001b[39m Listing \u001b[1m2\u001b[m\u000f directoriesвҖҰ \u001b[37m(ctrl+o to expand)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[37m\u001b[41;101H  вҺҝ  $ ls -la /workspace/pm-test-rec/pm/qa/ 2>&1; ls -la /workspace/pm-test-rec/ 2>&1\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[42;101H\u001b[K\u001b[31m\n*\u001b[39m \u001b[31mHarmoniz\u001b[93ming\u001b[31mвҖҰ \u001b[37m(8s В· вҶ‘\u001b[39m \u001b[37m308 tokens В· thinking with medium effort)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[44;101H\u001b[K\u001b[37m\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[37m\u001b[46;10"]
[34.589404, "o", "1HвқҜВ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[m\u000f\u001b[K\u001b[37m\u001b[47;101Hв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[48;101H  \u001b[37mesc\u001b[39m \u001b[37mto\u001b[39m \u001b[37minterrupt\u001b[39m                                                             \u001b[37mв—җ\u001b[39m \u001b[37mmedium\u001b[39m \u001b[37mВ·\u001b[39m \u001b[37m/effort\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[49;101H\u001b[K\u001b[30m\u001b[42m\r\n[pm-pm-tes0:main*                                                                                                                                                         \"a4caa0409360\" 21:24 13-May-26\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[1;51H\u001b[34h\u001b[?25h\u001b[?1006l\u001b[?1003l\u001b[?2004l"]
