[34.681457, "o", "в”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m                                                       \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[26;1H  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/`. |\u001b[39m                                                                \r\n  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks list/show/add/edit` | CLI for `pm/qa/mocks/`. |\u001b[39m                                   \r\n  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks prompt` | Prints the block injected into every QA scenario prompt. |\u001b[39m              \r\n             "]
[34.681463, "o", "                                                                                      \r\n  \u001b[97m## Authoring tips\u001b[39m                                                                                \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n  \u001b[97m- For artifact recipes, the manifest format section is the most\u001b[39m                                  \r\n  \u001b[97m  load-bearing part вҖ” make it unambiguous so captures aren't opaque.\u001b[39m                             \r\n  \u001b[97m- Recipes can reference your project's own paths and tooling freely вҖ”\u001b[39m                            \r\n  \u001b[97m  the QA library is per-project. Only extract something into a recipe\u001b[39m                            \r\n  \u001b[97m  if you'll reuse it across multiple scenarios or PRs.\u001b[39m                                           \r\n  \u001b[97m- `pm qa list` shows existing recipes; `pm qa show <id>` prints any\u001b[39m                              \r\n  \u001b[97m  one of them. Browse a few before authoring so"]
[34.68147, "o", "mething new вҖ” the\u001b[39m                                 \r\n  \u001b[97m  fastest way to learn the shape is to read what's already there.\u001b[39m                                \r\n                                                                                                   \r\n                                                                                                   \u001b[49m\u001b[42;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\r\n \u001b[39m Listing \u001b[1m2\u001b[m\u000f directoriesвҖҰ \u001b[37m(ctrl+o to expand)\u001b[39m                                                        \u001b[37m\r\n  вҺҝ  $ ls -la /workspace/pm-test-rec/pm/qa/ 2>&1; ls -la /workspace/pm-test-rec/ 2>&1\u001b[39m              \u001b[45;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[31m\r\nвң¶\u001b[39m \u001b[31mHarmonizi\u001b[93mngвҖҰ\u001b[31m \u001b[37m(8s В· вҶ‘\u001b[39m \u001b[37m308 tokens В· thinking with medium effort)\u001b[39m                                   \u001b[47;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\r\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ"]
