[34.701958, "o", "\u001b[26;1H\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mregression test\u001b[39m                                \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mpm qa author-artifact <name>        # new \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97martifact recipe\u001b[39m                                \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m```\u001b[39m                                            \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m                                                 \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mEach loads this document and walks the user \u001b[39m   \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mthrough drafting the file\u001b[39m                      \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mat the right path. If you'd rather just edit a\u001b[39m \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m stub yourself, the\u001b[39m                       "]
[34.702026, "o", "     \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m`pm qa add-instruction` / `add-regression` / \u001b[39m  \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m`add-artifact` siblings\u001b[39m                        \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mscaffold a stub and open `$EDITOR`.\u001b[39m            \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m                                                 \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m## File format (instructions / regression / \u001b[39m   \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97martifacts)\u001b[39m                                     \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m                                                 \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mEach `.md` file is YAML frontmatter followed \u001b[39m  \r\n  \u001b[97mby Markdown body:\u001b[39m                              \u001b[49m     "]
[34.702056, "o", "                                             \r\n\u001b[40m                                                 \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97m```text\u001b[39m                                        \r\n  \u001b[97m---\u001b[39m                                            \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mtitle: Login flow setup\u001b[39m                        \r\n  \u001b[97mdescription: Seed a test user and log them in \u001b[39m \u001b[49m                                                  \r\n\u001b[40m  \u001b[97mbef\u001b[39m                                            \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[1;101H"]
[34.702082, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[26;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-regression <name>` | Guided \u001b[39m   \u001b[49m\u001b[27;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mauthoring for a regression test. |\u001b[39m             \u001b[49m\u001b[28;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| `pm qa author-artifact <name>` | Guided \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m\u001b[29;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mauthoring for an artifact recipe. |\u001b[39m            \u001b[49m\u001b[30;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| `pm qa docs` | Prints this document. |\u001b[39m       \r\n  \u001b[97m| QA planner prompt | \u001b[39m                         \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[32;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m`instruction_summary_for_prompt` renders `### \u001b[39m \u001b[49m\u001b[33;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mInstructions` and `### Artifact Recipes`. \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m\u001b[34;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mRecipes are referenced by filename in the \u001b[39m     \u001b[49m\u001b[35;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mscenario `INSTRUCTION:` field. |\u001b[39m               \u001b[49m\u001b[36;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| Scenario 0 prompt | Same library summary, \u001b[39m   \u001b[49m\u001b[37;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mscoped to the interactive session. |\u001b[39m           \u001b[49m\u001b[38;"]
[34.70212, "o", "99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| Bug-fix flow prompt | Points sessions at \u001b[39m    \u001b[49m\u001b[39;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/instructions/` and `pm/qa/artifacts/` \u001b[39m  \u001b[49m\u001b[40;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mby directory; sessions discover specific files\u001b[39m \u001b[49m\u001b[41;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m themselves. Captures go under \u001b[39m                \u001b[49m\u001b[42;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/pre-fix/` and \u001b[39m    \r\n  \u001b[97m`вҖҰ/post-fix/`. |\u001b[39m                               \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[44;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| Bug-fix review checklist | Tells reviewers \u001b[39m  \u001b[49m\u001b[45;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97mto read captures under \u001b[39m                        \u001b[49m\u001b[46;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/captures/<pr-id>/impl/`. |\u001b[39m              \u001b[49m\u001b[47;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks list/show/add/edit` | CLI for \u001b[39m  \r\n  \u001b[97m`pm/qa/mocks/`. |\u001b[39m                              \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[49;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m| `pm qa mocks \u001b[m\u000f\u001b[34h\u001b[?25h\u001b[1;101H"]
[34.702149, "o", "\u001b[?25l\u001b[26;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m  the QA library is per-project. Only extract \u001b[39m \u001b[49m\u001b[27;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97msomething into a recipe\u001b[39m                        \u001b[49m\u001b[28;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m  if you'll reuse it across multiple scenarios\u001b[39m \r\n  \u001b[97m or PRs.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[30;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m- `pm qa list` shows existing recipes; `pm qa \u001b[39m \r\n  \u001b[97mshow <id>` prints any\u001b[39m                          \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[32;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m  one of them. Browse a few before authoring \u001b[39m  \r\n  \u001b[97msomething new вҖ” the\u001b[39m                            \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[34;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[40m\r  \u001b[97m  fastest way to learn the shape is to read \u001b[39m   \r\n  \u001b[97mwhat's already there.\u001b[39m                          \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[40m\r\n                                                 \u001b[49m                   "]
[34.702174, "o", "                               \u001b[40m\r\n                                                 \u001b[49m                                                  \u001b[38;99H\u001b[1K\n\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\r \u001b[39m Listing \u001b[1m2\u001b[m\u000f directoriesвҖҰ \u001b[37m(ctrl+o\u001b[39m \u001b[37mto\u001b[39m \u001b[37mexpand)\u001b[39m\u001b[40;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\r \u001b[39m \u001b[37mвҺҝ\u001b[39m  \u001b[37m$\u001b[39m \u001b[37mls\u001b[39m \u001b[37m-la\u001b[39m \u001b[37m/workspace/pm-test-rec/pm/qa/\u001b[39m \u001b[37m2>&1;\u001b[39m\u001b[41;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[5G\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\u001b[C ls\u001b[39m \u001b[37m-la\u001b[39m \u001b[37m/workspace/pm-test-rec/\u001b[39m \u001b[37m2>&1\u001b[39m\u001b[42;99H\u001b[1K\n\u001b[1K\u001b[31m\rвң¶\u001b[39m \u001b[31mHarmonizi\u001b[93mngвҖҰ\u001b[31m \u001b[37m(thinking\u001b[39m \u001b[37mwith\u001b[39m \u001b[37mmedium\u001b[39m \u001b[37meffort)\u001b[39m\u001b[44;99H\u001b[1K\n\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\rв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[46;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\rвқҜВ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[m\u000f\u001b[47;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\rв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[48;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[2G\u001b[1K\u001b[37m"]
