[37.462148, "o", "\u001b[40m\u001b[1;101H  \u001b[97mTo interact with this session, use commands like:\u001b[39m                                                 \u001b[2;101H  \u001b[97m- pm tui view -s pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1\u001b[39m                                                          \u001b[3;101H  \u001b[97m- pm tui send <keys> -s pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1\u001b[39m                                                   \u001b[4;101H  \u001b[97m- tmux list-panes -t pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1 -F \"#{pane_id} #{pane_width}x#{pane_height} \u001b[39m         \u001b[5;101H  \u001b[97m#{pane_current_command}\"\u001b[39m                                                                          \u001b[6;101H  \u001b[97m- cat ~/.pm/pane-registry/pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1.json\u001b[39m                                            \u001b[7;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[8;101H  \u001b[97m## Captures\u001b[39m                                                                                       \u001b[9;101H                                                                             "]
[37.462171, "o", "                       \u001b[10;101H  \u001b[97mAny capture you produce should land under `pm/qa/captures/regression/<test-id>/<timestamp>/`\u001b[39m      \u001b[11;101H  \u001b[97mand be committed (and pushed, if there's a remote) so future runs can\u001b[39m                             \u001b[12;101H  \u001b[97mdiff against this one. Use `git add pm/qa/captures/regression/.../`,\u001b[39m                              \u001b[13;101H  \u001b[97m`git commit -m \"qa: regression capture <test-id>\"`, then push.\u001b[39m                                    \u001b[14;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[15;101H  \u001b[97m## QA Regression Test: Test regression\u001b[39m                                                            \u001b[16;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[17;101H  \u001b[97mHello\u001b[39m                                                                                             \u001b[18;101H                                                            "]
[37.462178, "o", "                                        \u001b[19;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[20;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[21;101H  \u001b[97m## Filing Findings\u001b[39m                                                                                \u001b[22;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[23;101H  \u001b[97mFor each issue you observed, file a PR вҖ” don't fix it here.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[24;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[25;101H  \u001b[97m- **Bug**: `pm pr add '<title>' --plan bugs --description '<location, repro, expected vs \u001b[39m         \u001b[26;101H  \u001b[97mactual>'`\u001b[39m                                                                                         \u001b[27;101H  \u001b[97m- **Improvement**: `pm pr add '<title>' --plan improve"]
[37.462185, "o", "ments --description '<what you noticed and \u001b[39m \u001b[28;101H  \u001b[97mwhy>'`\u001b[39m                                                                                            \u001b[29;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[30;101H  \u001b[97mIf a capture under `pm/qa/captures/regression/...` demonstrates the\u001b[39m                               \u001b[31;101H  \u001b[97mfinding, point at the path in the description.\u001b[39m                                                    \u001b[32;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[33;101H  \u001b[97mSkim `pm pr list --plan bugs` / `--plan improvements` first. If a PR\u001b[39m                              \u001b[34;101H  \u001b[97mfor the same issue exists, append a note instead of filing a\u001b[39m                                      \u001b[35;101H  \u001b[97mduplicate: `pm pr note add <pr-id> '<short observation>; capture: <path>'`.\u001b[39m                       \u001b[36;101H                                  "]
[37.462192, "o", "                                                                  \u001b[37;101H  \u001b[97mFiling is independent of your verdict for the test.\u001b[39m                                               \u001b[38;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[39;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[49m\u001b[40;101H\u001b[K\u001b[97m\nв—Ҹ\u001b[39m Hello! How can I help you today?\u001b[K\u001b[42;101H\u001b[K\u001b[31m\n*\u001b[39m \u001b[31mPrestidigitati\u001b[93mngвҖҰ\u001b[31m \u001b[37m(2s В· вҶ“\u001b[39m \u001b[37m39 tokens В· thinking with medium effort)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[44;101H\u001b[K\u001b[37m\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[46;101HвқҜВ \u001b[39m\u001b[7m \u001b[m\u000f\u001b[K\u001b[37m\u001b[47;101Hв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ"]
