[41.053699, "o", "xit\u001b[39m \u001b[37mcode.\u001b[39m \u001b[37mBest\u001b[39m \u001b[37mwhen\u001b[39m \u001b[37mthe\u001b[39m \u001b[37mrun\u001b[39m \u001b[37misn't\u001b[39m     \u001b[43;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[5G\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\u001b[Canimated.\u001b[39m\u001b[44;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[2G\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\u001b[C5.\u001b[39m \u001b[37mType\u001b[39m \u001b[37msomething.\r\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[46;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[2G\u001b[1K\u001b[C6. Chat about this\u001b[47;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[37m\r\nEnter\u001b[39m \u001b[37mto\u001b[39m \u001b[37mselect\u001b[39m \u001b[37mВ·\u001b[39m \u001b[37mTab/Arrow\u001b[39m \u001b[37mkeys\u001b[39m \u001b[37mto\u001b[39m \u001b[37mnavigate\u001b[39m \u001b[37mВ·\u001b[39m \u001b[37mEsc\u001b[39m \u001b[37mto\u001b[39m \u001b[37mcancel\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[49;99H\u001b[1K\u001b[1;3H"]
[44.854671, "o", "\u001b[48;181H\u001b[K\u001b[49;103H\u001b[37mtmux\u001b[Cfocus-events\u001b[Coff\u001b[CВ·\u001b[Cadd\u001b[C'set\u001b[C-g\u001b[Cfocus-events\u001b[Con'\u001b[Cto\u001b[C~/.tmux.conf\u001b[Cand\u001b[Creattach\u001b[Cfor\u001b[Cfocus\u001b[CtraвҖҰ\u001b[1;3H\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[40m\u001b[98C  \u001b[97m- pm tui view -s pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1\u001b[39m                                                          \u001b[2;101H  \u001b[97m- pm tui send <keys> -s pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1\u001b[39m                                                   \u001b[3;101H  \u001b[97m- tmux list-panes -t pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1 -F \"#{pane_id} #{pane_width}x#{pane_height} \u001b[39m         \u001b[4;101H  \u001b[97m#{pane_current_command}\"\u001b[39m                                                                          \u001b[5;101H  \u001b[97m- cat ~/.pm/pane-registry/pm-pm-test-rec-dcd554c1.json\u001b[39m                                            \u001b[6;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[7;101H  \u001b[97m## Captures\u001b[39m                                                                                       \u001b[8;101H                                 "]
[44.854708, "o", "                                                                   \u001b[9;101H  \u001b[97mAny capture you produce should land under `pm/qa/captures/regression/<test-id>/<timestamp>/`\u001b[39m      \u001b[10;101H  \u001b[97mand be committed (and pushed, if there's a remote) so future runs can\u001b[39m                             \u001b[11;101H  \u001b[97mdiff against this one. Use `git add pm/qa/captures/regression/.../`,\u001b[39m                              \u001b[12;101H  \u001b[97m`git commit -m \"qa: regression capture <test-id>\"`, then push.\u001b[39m                                    \u001b[13;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[14;101H  \u001b[97m## QA Regression Test: Test regression\u001b[39m                                                            \u001b[15;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[16;101H  \u001b[97mHello\u001b[39m                                                                                             \u001b[17;101H                 "]
[44.854714, "o", "                                                                                   \u001b[18;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[19;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[20;101H  \u001b[97m## Filing Findings\u001b[39m                                                                                \u001b[21;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[22;101H  \u001b[97mFor each issue you observed, file a PR вҖ” don't fix it here.\u001b[39m                                       \u001b[23;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[24;101H  \u001b[97m- **Bug**: `pm pr add '<title>' --plan bugs --description '<location, repro, expected vs \u001b[39m         \u001b[25;101H  \u001b[97mactual>'`\u001b[39m                                                                                         \u001b[26;101H  \u001b[97m- **Improve"]
[44.854724, "o", "ment**: `pm pr add '<title>' --plan improvements --description '<what you noticed and \u001b[39m \u001b[27;101H  \u001b[97mwhy>'`\u001b[39m                                                                                            \u001b[28;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[29;101H  \u001b[97mIf a capture under `pm/qa/captures/regression/...` demonstrates the\u001b[39m                               \u001b[30;101H  \u001b[97mfinding, point at the path in the description.\u001b[39m                                                    \u001b[31;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[32;101H  \u001b[97mSkim `pm pr list --plan bugs` / `--plan improvements` first. If a PR\u001b[39m                              \u001b[33;101H  \u001b[97mfor the same issue exists, append a note instead of filing a\u001b[39m                                      \u001b[34;101H  \u001b[97mduplicate: `pm pr note add <pr-id> '<short observation>; capture: <path>'`.\u001b[39m                       "]
[44.854728, "o", "\u001b[35;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[36;101H  \u001b[97mFiling is independent of your verdict for the test.\u001b[39m                                               \u001b[37;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[38;101H                                                                                                    \u001b[49m\u001b[39;101H\u001b[K\u001b[97m\nв—Ҹ\u001b[39m Hello! How can I help you today?\u001b[K\u001b[41;101H\u001b[K\u001b[37m\nвң»\u001b[39m \u001b[37mCooked for 2s\u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[43;101H\u001b[K\u001b[37m\nв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ\u001b[39m\u001b[45;101HвқҜВ \u001b[7mw\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[2mhat can you help me with?\u001b[m\u000f\u001b[K\u001b[37m\u001b[46;101Hв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җ"]
